@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_yuvrhu(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = 0.44
    v2 = (0.89 / v0)
    tmp = wp.cos(tmp)
    v1 = wp.sin(0.24)
    v0 = (v0 - ((v2 + 0.05 / v2 + 0.01) + wp.abs(v1 + 0.84)))
    tmp = wp.sin(0.55)
    tmp = 0.05
    v0 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
